			</div>
		    
		    <div>
				<p>
					The article discusses repatriation of Burmese refugees from Thailand, which started in October 2016.
					It also provides a brief overview of the refugees who have been living in Thailand for over 30 years now. 
					It goes on to mention that while repatriation might be taking place it is unlikely that a large group of refugees will go back to Burma
					since the political situation there is still precarious for these people.
				</p>
