				</div>
				
			<div>
				<p>
					The article produced by the UNHCR provides some details of the refugees who left Thailand to reutrn to Myanmar. 
					It is focused on the Nupo refugee camp in Thailand and discusses the stories of different refugees who returned.
					Those returning express a mixture of hope and anxiety on their return, some are worried about finding jobs while others have been planning for this moment for a while. 
				</p>
